reviewText: Okay, I'll admit it: I love these two movies. "Bill & Ted" is so utterly silly and dumb that if you don't laugh, you're taking life way too seriously. I'm not addicted to "Dude . . . ," but it makes this DVD an excellent double-header for an evening when you just want to relax. Keanu Reeves looks about 14 years old, which makes sense. At his age now (50-ish?), he looks 35. Must be that red pill.
